title: Kloned! - A Kontemporary Kollection From Kloned Rekords  (1993)
description:
Who said music couldn&#039;t be KLONED?

I bought this back in 1993 from a good friend at Imports Etc. records in Chicago.  His name is Floyd.  I dedicate this collection in his memory, as I played it to death!

This is a collectors item - the first Kloned collection.  Klone Records followed in the steps of Almighty Records in the early 90&#039;s.  

Enjoy this!
